    "text": "EX-99.1\n2\ntm266226d2_ex99-1.htm\nEXHIBIT 99.1\n\n \n\nExhibit 99.1\n\n \n\n \n Date: February 13, 2026\n \n \n 510 Burrard Street, 3rd Floor\nVancouver BC, V6C 3B9\nwww.computershare.com\n \n \n\nTo: All Canadian Securities Regulatory Authorities\n\nSubject: ELDORADO GOLD CORPORATION\n\n \n\nDear Sir/Madam:\n\n \n\nWe advise of the following with respect to the upcoming Meeting of\nSecurity Holders for the subject Issuer:\n\n \n\n \n Meeting Type :\n \n Special Meeting\n \n Record Date for Notice of Meeting :\n \n March 03, 2026\n \n Record Date for Voting (if applicable) :\n \n March 03, 2026\n \n Beneficial Ownership Determination Date :\n \n March 03, 2026\n \n Meeting Date :\n \n April 07, 2026\n \n Meeting Location (if available) :\n \n Vancouver, BC\n \n Issuer sending proxy related materials directly to NOBO: \n \n No\n \n Issuer paying for delivery to OBO:\n \n Yes\n \n Notice and Access (NAA) Requirements:\n \n \n \n NAA for Beneficial Holders\n \n No\n \n NAA for Registered Holders\n \n No\n \n \n\nVoting Security Details:\n\n \n\n \n Description\n CUSIP Number\n ISIN\n \n COMMON SHARES\n 284902509\n CA2849025093\n \n \n\nSincerely,\n\n \n\nComputershare\n\nAgent for ELDORADO GOLD CORPORATION",
