    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>tm266226d2_ex99-1.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>EXHIBIT 99.1\n<TEXT>\n<HTML>\n<HEAD>\n     <TITLE></TITLE>\n</HEAD>\n<BODY STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif\">\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: right\"><B>Exhibit 99.1</B></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0pt 0\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<TABLE CELLSPACING=\"0\" CELLPADDING=\"0\" STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse\">\n  <TR>\n    <TD ROWSPAN=\"2\" STYLE=\"font-size: 10pt\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Times New Roman, Times, Serif; font-size: 10pt\">Date: February&nbsp;13, 2026</FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"white-space: nowrap; vertical-align: top; width: 2in; font-size: 10pt\"><IMG SRC=\"tm266226d2_ex99-1img001.jpg\" ALT=\"\"></TD></TR>\n  <TR STYLE=\"vertical-align: top\">\n    <TD STYLE=\"white-space: nowrap; font-size: 10pt\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Times New Roman, Times, Serif; font-size: 10pt\">510 Burrard Street, 3rd Floor<BR>\nVancouver BC, V6C 3B9<BR>\n<U>www.computershare.com</U></FONT></TD></TR>\n  </TABLE>\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0pt 0\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0pt 0\">To: All Canadian Securities Regulatory Authorities</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0pt 0\"><B>Subject: ELDORADO GOLD CORPORATION</B></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0pt 0\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0pt 0\">Dear Sir/Madam:</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0pt 0\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0pt 0\">We advise of the following with respect to the upcoming Meeting of\nSecurity Holders for the subject Issuer:</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0pt 0\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<TABLE CELLSPAC